item.description: ABU DHABI, UAE, Dec. 19, 2025 /PRNewswire/ -- Abu Dhabi Finance Week (ADFW) 2025, held under the patronage of His Highness Sheikh Khaled bin Mohamed bin Zayed Al Nahyan, Crown Prince of Abu Dhabi and Chairman of the Abu Dhabi Executive Council concluded after a momentous week of dynamic discussions,...
